  "texts": [
    "We then build a 2SLS estimator on top of the learned features.",
    "The same qualitative trends are observed: MSE decreases with slower singular value decay and better alignment.",
    "Moreover, when c σ is small (top rows), learning the entire eigenspaces becomes difficult.",
    "In this regime, performance is most sensitive to c α.",
    "In particular, if h 0 is concentrated on the top singular functions (small c α), good recovery is still possible."
